(144, '_site_transient_wp_plugin_dependencies_plugin_data', 'a:1:{s:14:\"contact-form-7\";a:35:{s:4:\"name\";s:14:\"Contact Form 7\";s:4:\"slug\";s:14:\"contact-form-7\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"6.0.2\";s:6:\"author\";s:62:\"<a href=\"https://ideasilo.wordpress.com/\">Takayuki Miyoshi</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:12:\"takayukister\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:120:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/538487024e649d43dea84ff38d14582d03119e3e7aaaca3b7692443335999133?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Takayuki Miyoshi\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"6.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.7.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:16:\"requires_plugins\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1431;i:4;i:146;i:3;i:75;i:2;i:68;i:1;i:403;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:2123;s:11:\"support_url\";s:52:\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\";s:15:\"support_threads\";i:154;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:38;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2024-12-22 5:03am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2007-08-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:25:\"https://contactform7.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:2613:\"<p>Contact Form 7 is a plugin designed to be a practical tool for all WordPress users who embrace the philosophy of free and open source software. It employs sophisticatedly modularized architecture and its original <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/schema-woven-validation/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Schema-Woven Validation</a> technology.</p>\n<h4>Documents et support</h4>\n<p>You can find <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">docs</a>, <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a> and more detailed information about Contact Form 7 on <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contactform7.com</a>. When you cannot find the answer to your question on the FAQ or in any of the documentation, check the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">support forum</a> on WordPress.org. If you cannot locate any topics that pertain to your particular issue, post a new topic for it.</p>\n<h4>Contact Form 7 a besoin de vous</h4>\n<p>It is hard to continue to maintain this plugin without support from users like you. There are several ways for you to <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contributing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contribute to the project</a>: testing, coding, translating it into your local languages, helping other users, financial donations, etc, etc. We equally welcome you regardless of the way you contribute.</p>\n<h4>Avis de confidentialité</h4>\n<p>Avec la configuration par défaut, cette extension, ne :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Suivre les utilisateurs/utilisatrices furtivement ;</li>\n<li>Inscrire toutes les données des utilisatrices et utilisateurs dans la base de données ;</li>\n<li>Envoyer les données aux serveurs externes</li>\n<li>utilise les cookies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Si vous activez certaines fonctionnalités de cette extension, les données personnelles de l&rsquo;expéditeur ou de l’expéditrice du formulaire de contact, y compris son adresse IP, peuvent être envoyées au fournisseur de service. Par conséquent, il est recommandé de confirmer la politique de confidentialité du fournisseur. Ces fonctionnalités incluent :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href=\"https://policies.google.com/?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>Akismet (<a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Automatique</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.constantcontact.com/legal/privacy-center\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Constant Contact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Brevo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stripe.com/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stripe</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:512:\"<ol>\n<li>Mettez en ligne le dossier complet <code>contact-form-7</code> dans le répertoire <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code>.</li>\n<li>Activer l’extension via l’écran <strong>Extensions</strong> (<strong>Extensions &gt; Extensions installées</strong>).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Vous trouverez le menu <strong>Contact</strong> dans votre écran d’administration WordPress.</p>\n<p>Pour un usage pratique, vous pouvez consulter le <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">site de l’extension</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:494:\"<p>Vous avez une question ou un problème avec Contact Form 7? Utilisez ces sources de supports de façon appropriée.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Forum de support</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/support/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Support</a></p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1571:\"<p>Pour plus d&rsquo;informations, consultez <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/category/releases/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Versions</a>.</p>\n<h4>6.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removes unnecessary type declaration from nullable arguments to avoid deprecation warnings in PHP 8.4.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.1</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.7</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.6</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.5</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.4</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.3</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.2</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/</a></p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:225:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\" alt=\"screenshot-1.png\"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17882:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple yet Affective Contact Form.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danishalionline/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3874b75f6231dd375e4a6960595a54282269b39c5f644b94b3ff89d8e03cbd0e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3874b75f6231dd375e4a6960595a54282269b39c5f644b94b3ff89d8e03cbd0e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danishalionline/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Danish Ali <small>(danishalionline)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 9, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the one plugin i used o my every wordpress site. its keeps getting better. However we would to see some more features like Calender and recapthca implementation with this form with ease. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Dude what happened</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Alex Freixa <small>(alexfreixa)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 3, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Why it\'s unusable? This plugin was working so fine. Customize it it\'s a nightmare!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lack of support, lack of accessibility</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">heggyy</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">janvier 3, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Overhyped plugin simply because it is free. It is the ultimate barebones of a plugin that people find necessary. There are no features, customizing anything means you are either a) a programmer or b) have to email support (in which case good luck getting help, egos too big). Gets no updates, no features, no accessibility or UX improvements. You\'re better off paying for a plugin than pulling your hair out to get it working as needed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">quick resposne to questions and support tickets</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frankyuyong/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e256a8b26bc82e4a27d420c11998d37300d62eeba2f3adcd1adc3daa7398722e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e256a8b26bc82e4a27d420c11998d37300d62eeba2f3adcd1adc3daa7398722e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frankyuyong/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">frankyuyong</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">décembre 11, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The team is highly responsive and helpful. They arranged a Google Meet session to assist me with an API and JSON data format issue, thoroughly resolving the problem on my end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">not working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yosragattoufi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/408c84ff4582155ccee988521d17f0f786153d528d06a500808b644061dd5790?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/408c84ff4582155ccee988521d17f0f786153d528d06a500808b644061dd5790?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yosragattoufi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yosragattoufi</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">décembre 4, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hello,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For recaptcha It is not working for us since 2 years. we redesigned the website and it still not working.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When someone submit the form he has an eeror message that the message could not be sent , or it still loading without submission.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am using the part \"Integration\" on contact form 7</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Translation issue and nightmare support.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jyria/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3ffa0afd56f0b53fb075f65fa2657a765d4790567818a3f2c6ac0e2a1126066?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3ffa0afd56f0b53fb075f65fa2657a765d4790567818a3f2c6ac0e2a1126066?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jyria/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Saskia Teichmann <small>(Jyria)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 26, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This free plugin is very useful and has done what it was supposed to do for many years. However, there are a few issues that are very annoying and a total deal breaker, if not a show stopper:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Plugin creator did not comply with WordPress Codex regarding how translations are handled. Thus this plugin will eventually cause problems in a multilingual site.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Forum support by plugin creator is very poor. He replies, yes, but his replies are a joke. He simply doesn\'t care. He doesn\'t read properly nor does he do any testing, even after providing everything he asked for. He is a time stealer.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My personal resume: I will switch contact forms on all of my clients\' sites. There are better alternatives out there. I am of course willing to pay for support. And this is my suggestion for @takayukister : provide paid support, if you think your time is too valuable, to give a useful reply or provide assistance with your free plugin. Or take that plugin offline or officially state that you won\'t provide support at all and refrain from stealing people\'s time by requesting non sense things and then ignoring them in return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Horrendous, overcomplicated plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davepez/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82710dca0a6524a1bf7c9249795a8f061613e5bb93e57ce8cbae6802f465f528?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82710dca0a6524a1bf7c9249795a8f061613e5bb93e57ce8cbae6802f465f528?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davepez/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davepez</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 24, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve had problems with this plugin for years.  It can appear simple at first but so many times has required a load of custom code to sort the formatting properly and to get it looking right on all devices.  This always takes ages - googling it and finding loads of other people posting that they can\'t do simple things and never any solution.  It should not require so much fannying about!  The support website is useless, too.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Flexible and Reliable Plugin with Great Anti-Spam Features</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mojcak/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0013f2a939ed42fe21ae2274c85e31b57ef7e3b2ebdd2714265a119bb2ebf3d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0013f2a939ed42fe21ae2274c85e31b57ef7e3b2ebdd2714265a119bb2ebf3d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mojcak/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mojcak</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 23, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact Form 7 is incredibly versatile and adaptable, making it easy to create custom forms for a variety of needs. One of my favorite features is the math-based spam protection, which works very effectively without adding unnecessary complexity. The plugin has been a reliable choice for all my projects. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a robust form solution!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">New Version responsive issue.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sknasib/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccfeae62d49c8bde406f2837882bac00827771c98b3d0cf5eb6e60bce266c3d4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccfeae62d49c8bde406f2837882bac00827771c98b3d0cf5eb6e60bce266c3d4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sknasib/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Sk Nasib Alam <small>(sknasib)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 22, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Field add Window, Header Button and Footer Button option not showing. When I set the screen Size 80% then those options are showing. Big issue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Need WP Consent API to integrate with Complianz</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/carlodamo/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d458d14020e19716d2d66db583ac7c86e344286e392a1a2b55e952b026cb2b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d458d14020e19716d2d66db583ac7c86e344286e392a1a2b55e952b026cb2b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/carlodamo/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">carlodamo</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 21, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please, add WP Consent API to integrate with Complianz.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:83:\"Juste une autre extension de formulaire de contact. Simple et facilement adaptable.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.6.0.2.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/contact-